{"id":4492,"date":"2013-10-10T00:49:47","date_gmt":"2013-10-09T23:49:47","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/altlab.org\/?p=4492"},"modified":"2013-10-10T00:49:47","modified_gmt":"2013-10-09T23:49:47","slug":"workshop-controlo-de-motores-dc-passo-servo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/2013\/10\/10\/workshop-controlo-de-motores-dc-passo-servo\/","title":{"rendered":"Workshop Controlo de Motores [<span class=\"caps\">DC<\/span>, Passo, Servo]"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3><a href=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/2013\/10\/10\/workshop-controlo-de-motores-dc-passo-servo\/#WCDM\"><strong>Mais informa\u00e7\u00f5es e inscri\u00e7\u00f5es<br>\n<\/strong><br>\n<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"542\" height=\"837\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4493\" alt=\"Workshop Controlo de Motores\" src=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/10\/workshops-altlab-flyer_CTRL-MOTORES_19Out.jpg\"><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><!--more--><br>\n<\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><a name=\"WCDM\"><\/a><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Workshop Controlo de Motores [<span class=\"caps\">DC<\/span>, Passo e&nbsp;Servo]<\/h4>\n<p>Ok, j\u00e1 des\u00admon\u00adtas\u00adte impres\u00adso\u00adras e scan\u00adners, cani\u00adba\u00adli\u00adzas\u00adte brin\u00adque\u00addos e \u2018sacas\u00adte\u2019 motores.<br>\nE&nbsp;agora?<\/p>\n<p>Exis\u00adtem mui\u00adtos tipos de moto\u00adres mas nes\u00adte workshop con\u00adcen\u00adtra\u00admo-nos naque\u00adles que saca\u00admos dos equi\u00adpa\u00admen\u00adtos mori\u00adbun\u00addos e pode\u00admos re-uti\u00adli\u00adzar: moto\u00adres sim\u00adples de cor\u00adren\u00adte con\u00adt\u00ed\u00adnua (vul\u00adgo <span class=\"caps\">DC<\/span>), moto\u00adres de pas\u00adso (vul\u00adgo motor de pas\u00adso-a-pas\u00adso ou \u2018step\u00adper\u2019) e ser\u00advo de r\u00e1dio-con\u00adtro\u00adlo (vul\u00adgo ser\u00advo&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\">RC<\/span>).<br>\nImpres\u00adso\u00adras <span class=\"caps\">3D<\/span>, m\u00e1qui\u00adnas <span class=\"caps\">CNC<\/span> (con\u00adtro\u00adlo num\u00e9\u00adri\u00adco com\u00adpu\u00adto\u00adri\u00adza\u00addo) e Robots, por exem\u00adplo, s\u00e3o pro\u00adjec\u00adtos mui\u00adto exi\u00adgen\u00adtes no que res\u00adpei\u00adta ao con\u00adtro\u00adlo do movi\u00admen\u00adto e neces\u00adsi\u00adtam de \u2018espre\u00admer\u2019 o motor ao seu limi\u00adte. \u00c9 aqui que entra o con\u00adcei\u00adto \u201cCon\u00adtro\u00adlo de Motores\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>Traz o teu Ardui\u00adno (ou um outro qual\u00adquer micro\u00adcon\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addor que pre\u00adfi\u00adras e domi\u00adnes) e vamos mexer em motores!<\/p>\n<p>Nes\u00adte workshop vamos ter Ardui\u00adnos, dri\u00advers e moto\u00adres para expe\u00adri\u00admen\u00adta\u00adres mas deves tra\u00adzer o teu por\u00adt\u00e1\u00adtil j\u00e1 com o <span class=\"caps\">IDE<\/span> do teu micro\u00adcon\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addor ins\u00adta\u00adla\u00addo e a fun\u00adci\u00ado\u00adnar, ou o <span class=\"caps\">IDE<\/span> do Ardui\u00adno se qui\u00adse\u00adres expe\u00adri\u00admen\u00adtar um dos nos\u00adsos (link para down\u00adlo\u00adad gra\u00adtu\u00ed\u00adto, Mac, Win\u00addows ou Linux: <a title=\"IDE Arduino\" href=\"http:\/\/arduino.cc\/en\/Main\/Software\">http:\/\/arduino.cc\/en\/Main\/Software<\/a>).<\/p>\n<p><strong>Con\u00adcei\u00adtos abordados<\/strong><br>\n<em><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em> Cons\u00adti\u00adtui\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o interna:<\/em><br>\n\u2014 de um motor&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\">DC<\/span><br>\n\u2014 de um motor Passo-a-Passo<br>\n\u2014 de um Ser\u00advo\u00admo\u00adtor (Actu\u00ada\u00addor, Reduc\u00adto\u00adra, Enco\u00adder para Feed\u00adback e Controlo)<\/p>\n<p><em> Con\u00adcei\u00adtos l\u00f3gicos:<\/em><br>\n\u2014 do Con\u00adtro\u00adlo do motor&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\">DC<\/span><br>\n\u2014 do Con\u00adtro\u00adlo do motor Pas\u00adso-a-Pas\u00adso (Uni\u00adpo\u00adlar e Bipolar)<br>\n\u2014 do Con\u00adtro\u00adlo do Ser\u00advo\u00admo\u00adtor (comu\u00adni\u00adca\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es)<br>\n\u2014&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\">PWM<\/span><br>\n\u2014 Vari\u00ada\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o de frequ\u00eancia<br>\n\u2014 <span class=\"caps\">PID<\/span> (intro\u00addu\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o&nbsp;ao)<\/p>\n<p><em>Cir\u00adcui\u00adtos de controlo:<\/em><br>\n\u2014 Con\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addor de um canal (Sin\u00adgle chan\u00adnel dimmer\/ Sin\u00adgle motor dri\u00adver \u2014 one direction)<br>\n\u2014 Con\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addor de 4 canais (Four chan\u00adnel dimmer\/ uni\u00adpo\u00adlar step\u00adper driver)<br>\n\u2014 Con\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addor de 2 canais em pon\u00adte H: (Two chan\u00adnel driver\/ bipo\u00adlar step\u00adper driver)<\/p>\n<p><em>Exer\u00adc\u00ed\u00adci\u00ados:<\/em><br>\n\u2014 Expe\u00adri\u00ad\u00ean\u00adcia e apren\u00addi\u00adza\u00adgem \u2018hands-on\u2019 com micro\u00adcon\u00adtro\u00adla\u00addo\u00adres, dri\u00advers e os v\u00e1ri\u00ados tipos de moto\u00adres fornecidos.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\">Este work\u00adshop ser\u00e1 ori\u00aden\u00adtado <span class=\"GRspelling\">por<\/span> mem\u00adbros do altLab.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px;\">\n<strong>Ins\u00adcri\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es<\/strong> : <a href=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/event-registration\/#WCDM\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span class=\"caps\">AQUI<\/span><\/b> (a ins\u00adcri\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o on-line \u00e9 obrigat\u00f3ria)<\/a><br>\n<strong>Pre\u00ad\u00e7o<\/strong> : 30\u20ac. Mem\u00adbros do altLab s\u00f3 pagam 20\u20ac ;p<br>\n<strong>Local<\/strong> : no altLab, \u00e9 cla\u00adro! (<a href=\"http:\/\/maps.google.com\/maps\/ms?daddr=&amp;saddr=Praceta+Domingos+Rodrigues,+Loures+2685,+Portugal&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;doflg=ptk&amp;msa=0&amp;ll=38.784465,-9.127729&amp;spn=0.004382,0.010568&amp;t=h&amp;z=17&amp;msid=207816408522249587914.00049d2e29ed5bcfba45e\" target=\"_blank\">Pra\u00adce\